Interface PropertiesFileKeys

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ConfigurationFile

    public interface PropertiesFileKeys
    Keys for the properties file.
    Author:
    amedrano

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static String CONNECTION_MODE
      System property used to determine if the connection should be set up as a client (use value CLIENT) or as a server (use value SERVER).
      static String HASH_KEY
      The Key for encryption.
      static String REMOTE_HOST
      System property used for specifying remote AAL Space Gateways addresses that is running in Server Mode and that we should connect to
      static String SECURITY_DEFINITION
      System property that defines the turtle file that defines which imports, exports, and messages are allowed or denyed.
      static String SOCKET_PORT
      System property used for specifying the socket port of the AAL Space Gateway to connec to, in case that it is running in Server-Mode it is the socket to listen to.
